    {
      "description": "erika_cafe_monolog_2",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "如果是和老师一起的话，感觉会很有趣。",
      "text_original": "先生と一緒にやったら楽しそう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_cafe_monolog_2.ogg"
