      "text": "这个是老师的爱好吗？",
      "text_original": "これって先生の趣味なのかな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_cafe_monolog_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_cafe_monolog_4",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "（这个，是谁的呢？）",
      "text_original": "（これ、誰のなんだろ？）",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_cafe_monolog_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_cafe_monolog_5",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "嗯……？总觉得有人在盯着我。",
      "text_original": "ん……？なんか視線を感じる。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_cafe_monolog_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_commonskill",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "还能再坚持一下吗？",
      "text_original": "もうちょっと頑張れる？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_commonskill.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_eventlobby_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "我们学校的学生基本都不太安分，真是辛苦呢……。",
      "text_original": "うちの生徒ってあんまり落ち着きないから大変だよね……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_eventlobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_eventlobby_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "这样就没问题了……吧。",
      "text_original": "これで大丈夫、かな……。",
