    },
    {
      "description": "erika_formation_select",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "哇啊！？等一下老师……唉，先跟我说一声嘛。",
      "text_original": "わぁっ！？ちょっと先生……はぁ、先に言ってよね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_formation_select.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_gachaget",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "呀吼。格赫娜学园2年级，旗见绘里香。请多指教喽。",
