      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_growup_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "我说老师……那个，我还想再来一次呢。",
      "text_original": "ねえ先生……それ、またやってほしいな。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_growup_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "总觉得有点让人上瘾呢……可能稍微有点危险哦。",
      "text_original": "なんか中毒性あるんだよね……ちょっと危ないかも。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_growup_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "今天的值日生是我哦。有什么事随时跟我说。",
      "text_original": "今日の当番は私だよ。何かあったらいつでも言って。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师工作真的很努力呢。虽然看不太出来就是了。",
      "text_original": "先生って、仕事頑張ってるよね。あんまそうは見えないけど。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "哼哼……我只是觉得，努力的大人真的很帅气呢～而已。",
      "text_original": "ふふっ……頑張ってる大人ってカッコいいな～って、思っただけ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师为什么会一直当“老师”呢？总觉得，有点好奇……。",
      "text_original": "先生が「先生」を続けてるのってどうして？なんか、気になって……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "因为有想要守护的东西吗……哼嗯。",
      "text_original": "守るべきものがあるから、か……ふうん。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_3_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "那，你也会守护……我吗？",
      "text_original": "じゃあ私のことも……守ってくれる？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_3_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这边的文件已经处理完了哦。好累啊！",
      "text_original": "こっちの書類は終わったよ。結構キツかったー！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "不过，只要能帮上老师的忙就好了。",
      "text_original": "まぁ、先生の役に立ってるならいいんだけどさ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "嗯？豹纹？我喜欢啊。",
      "text_original": "ん？レオパード柄？好きだよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "喜欢到除了枪之外，还收集了很多豹纹图案的东西呢♪",
      "text_original": "銃以外にも色々レオパード柄で揃えたりしてるくらいにはね♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_lobby_5_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "其他还有什么豹纹的私人物品？呵呵……才～不告诉你呢♪",
      "text_original": "他に持ってるレオパード柄の私物？ふふっ……教えてあーげない♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_5_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_login_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "呀吼，老师♪我一直在等你哦。",
      "text_original": "やっほ、先生♪待ってたよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_login_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_login_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "欢迎回来！好想见你呀。",
      "text_original": "おかえり！会いたかった。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_login_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_login_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "（等一下……我刚才说了什么？）",
      "text_original": "（ちょっと待って……私今なんて？）",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_login_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "欢迎光临，老师。",
      "text_original": "ようこそ、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这里是，只属于我一个人的秘密基地——",
      "text_original": "ここが、私だけの秘密基地――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "想要独处的时候，就会过来的地方。",
      "text_original": "一人の時間が欲しい時に、来る場所。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "呵呵，不过要说是秘密基地的话，可能稍微宽敞了一点。",
      "text_original": "ふふっ、でも秘密基地っていうには、ちょっと広いかも。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……总觉得，想要和老师一起分享呢。",
      "text_original": "……なんか、先生に共有したかったんだよね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "比如我平时看到的风景……或者感受到的空气之类的。",
      "text_original": "私がいつも見ている景色とか……感じてる空気、とか。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "就算你问我理由，我也只能说是不知为何……",
      "text_original": "理由を聞かれてもなんとなく、しか言えないんだけど……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "是啊……因为把秘密场所告诉别人，就是特别的证明嘛。",
      "text_original": "そうだね……秘密の場所を教えるのって、特別の証だからさ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_4_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "也就是说，老师对我来说是特别的人。",
      "text_original": "先生は、私の特別な人ってこと。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_4_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……呵呵。",
      "text_original": "……ふふっ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这里很安静吧？",
      "text_original": "ここは静かでしょ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_memoriallobby_5_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "不过……我的内心，其实有点吵闹呢。",
      "text_original": "まあでも……私の心は、ちょっと騒がしいんだけどね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_5_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_relationship_up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "最近好像经常和老师见面？为什么呢。",
      "text_original": "最近先生とよく会うかも？なんでだろね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_relationship_up_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_relationship_up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "总觉得你送了我好多东西呢。虽然很高兴……但总是我在收礼也不太好吧。老师有什么想要的东西吗？",
      "text_original": "なんかいっぱいくれるじゃん。嬉しいけど……もらってばっかはなぁ。先生は欲しいもの、ある？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_relationship_up_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_relationship_up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "嗯——……感觉要上瘾了。请不要太娇惯我哦？会让我很困扰的。",
      "text_original": "んー……クセになりそ。あんまり甘やかさないでよ？困っちゃう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_relationship_up_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_relationship_up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "真是的……老师这么宠我，我都要被宠坏了。……真是的。总觉得只有我一个人在心动啊？",
      "text_original": "ほんとさ……先生が甘やかすからダメになっちゃいそ。……もう。私ばっかドキドキさせられてる気がするんだけど？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_relationship_up_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_season_birthday_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "诶……你记得我的生日吗？",
      "text_original": "えっ……私の誕生日、覚えてたの？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_birthday_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_season_birthday_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师真是个罪孽深重的人呢。……让我这么期待，你打算怎么负责？",
      "text_original": "先生って本当に罪づくりな人だよね。……期待、させちゃってどうする気？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_birthday_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_season_birthday_player",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师，生日快乐～！祝你度过比世界上任何人都要幸福的一天！",
      "text_original": "先生、お誕生日おめでと～！世界の誰よりも幸せな日でありますよーに！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_birthday_player.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_season_halloween_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "嗷呜——！不给糖就吃掉你哦！",
      "text_original": "ガオーッ！お菓子くれなきゃ食べちゃうぞ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_halloween_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_season_halloween_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "好啦，为了不被吃掉要好好努力哦。",
      "text_original": "ほら、食べられないように頑張って。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_halloween_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_season_newyear",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "新年快乐，老师！今年也要一起创造满满的回忆呢。",
      "text_original": "あけましておめでとう、先生！今年もいっぱい思い出作ろうね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_newyear.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_season_xmas_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "圣诞节是个好日子呢。总觉得气氛让人兴奋，又让人心跳加速……。",
      "text_original": "クリスマスっていい日だよね。雰囲気がワクワクするっていうか、ドキドキするっていうか……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_xmas_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_season_xmas_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "只是待在一起……就有特别的日子的感觉，对吧。",
      "text_original": "特別な日って感じ……一緒にいるだけで、ね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_xmas_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "erika_Title",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "蔚蓝档案！",
      "text_original": "ブルーアーカイブ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_Title.ogg"
    }
  ],
  "voice_cn": [],
  "voice_kr": [],
